data.description: Check out this gorgeous split-level in SE Minot's Bluffs Addition that surrounds the Country Club! This Dublin plan is constructed by quality builder RHR Construction. The inviting living room boasts a large boxed bay window and is open to the kitchen and dining. The kitchen has tons of custom cabinetry, an island, corner pantry and high definition countertops. The dining room provides an abundance of natural lighting with the unique curved turret creating a stately appeal inside and out! The master suite has plenty of space to relax & features a private bath and large walk-in closet. Also on the main are 2 additional bedrooms, a full bath & convenient main floor laundry! The daylight lower level is fully finished with a HUGE family room, bedrooms 4 & 5, a third full bath. There's also lots of storage with a bonus den/office and garage access from the mechanical room. Don't miss out on your chance to own this custom dream home!
